Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:12.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:17.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a hard fight, Luffy and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,defeated the Warlord - Donquixote Doflamingo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and left the fateful island, Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now become\NStraw Hat Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s followers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll be his shield \Nor pike in all weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To repay him for what he did \Nthis time, we seven will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...drink out of these Sons' \NCups of our own volition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,devoting our lives and souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're formally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and prepare for the banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the battle against the Mingo Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Numerous Rivals Struggle Amongst Themselves!\NThe Raging Monsters of the New World"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see Dressrosa anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You achieved your goal by taking \Ndown Doflamingo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find any list they \Nused for trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was all clearly stolen by somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the weapons and explosives \Nthat were left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were stolen after the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:43.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CIPHER POL "AIGIS" ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been some organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy was panicking about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the Revolutionary Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Who else would do that?\NCome back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're way out of line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going next, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the land of tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark strings were cast one after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Counting the number of tragedies \Nthat fell upon them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they hold back their tears \Nand play the music...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
