Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ol√©{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The curtain was drawn during the long, sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,nameless show without any applause{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then the words of truth reach them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The king has returned\Nand with peace ahead, all is serene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a preposition for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you for the introduction.\NI'm Chief Tonta, Gancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing next to me is my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mansherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to make this, Leo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Conference "Reverie" is this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like each country has \Nalready started preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca said she'll come to \Ncook for us this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?! What about Kyros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come, too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good. The whole family \Nwill gather together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Visitors to this kingdom will have\Nsomething to be amazed about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can I have a ham?\N--Oh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca and Mansherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"They" are blending in with the town{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and living side-by-side with humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. We haven't even \Nbuilt houses to live in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, this must be our first priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The visitors will be amazed\Nby these adorable Dwarves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a kingdom of love \Nand passion and fairies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. The statues must come first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,When we finish transporting the prisoner,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:49.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAVY'S FLEET
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without Straw Hat and Law's heads,\NI can't enter any Navy base so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just simply apologize,\NSakazuki can save face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have face to save, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an idiot, Tsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had sided with me\Nand helped me get rid of all those brats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't have ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was holding the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reins to the monsters of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have taken me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you people will regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such pathetic crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no "If."\NIt's crazy to even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This outcome is the only reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how can I best you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wolf knows what the ill beast thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen \Nto the world of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To answer your question\Nwith another question,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think the unleashed \Nmonsters who lost the "food"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I supplied them will do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone who is at the top \Nof the ladder in all the seas now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's ruling all the seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it one of the Four Emperors of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the Seven Warlords who cleverly live out\Nin the seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the brats from the Worst Generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy, the military forces of justice,\Nis conquering the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some strong members \Nwho we must keep an eye on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Revolutionary Army, \Nthe ally of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The family of "D." have been hiding\Nin the shadow of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When and where are they \Ngonna show themselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna side with who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna betray who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the Celestial Dragons\Nin the Holyland of Mariejois...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that they'll be dragged down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 25 years since Gold Roger \Nfully explored the whole Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His arch enemy, Whitebeard, \Ndidn't sit on the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but just stood in front \Nof it and took the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of pirates is ballooning
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's one seat that's totally empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest struggle for supremacy ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the history of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The mast has caught fire!\N--Put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to Impel Down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I need you to \Ngive me a newspaper everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I won't be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four Navy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the lineup is so formidable!\NAre they gonna go destroy a country?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They use so much force just for transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how great Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to take back Joker.\NCaptain Jack, shall we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! We're gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Look around as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Barto Club's pirate ship\Nthat's filled with love for the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Mister Luffy Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this right, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Luffy's on \Nthis ship more than ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you noticed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Straw Hats' first pirate ship
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a dear friend - the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I duplicated its bow as a homage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has evil eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take a good look at this curve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked a woodcrafter to \Nduplicate Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum hands just like the real ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, you have a good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's a homage \Nto Chopper-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those orange trees are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They're a homage to the orange trees that\NNami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,took from Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0}'s \Ngrove in Coco Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes oranges are just oranges!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sooo moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how nerdy those details are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere you look, you feel a sense of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with {\i1}super{\i0} love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Franky-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nerd has stirred a pervert's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anything,\Nwhat we're thrilled about now is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the direction this Vivre Card is\Npointing towards,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have the real Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!\NThank you again for coming on board this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! He's so dazzling! I can barely see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're all like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it was nice of Sabo\Nto make a Vivre Card of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I made a Vivre Card \Nof Luffy just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, when did you have time for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's my great Sabo-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so thoughtful and strong! What a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna become your follower but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna take it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll say goodbye for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you soon, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I had so much fun at the banquet!\NI like them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo, just hurry up and go to Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Leave it in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's head for Zou at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,\NI wonder if Sanji and the others got to the island safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami was with them so I'm \Nsure navigation was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were chased by Big Mom's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like our bounties have gone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have the wanted posters \Nof you all in my room so come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please!\N--Alright, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw out yours but your bounty \Nhas gone up to 500 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks. But I don't care about the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, please take a look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're in frames?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The autographs you gave \Nme earlier are there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BARTOLOMEO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO MY BROTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NICO ROBIN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:24.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start\Nwith "Straw Hat" Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bounty is 500 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 500 million! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"STRAW HAT" LUFFY -\N BOUNTY: 500 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:35.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, "Pirate Hunter" Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,320 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:42.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"PIRATE HUNTER" ZORO - \NBOUNTY: 320 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"Demon Child" Nico Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,130 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"DEMON CHILD" NICO ROBIN - \NBOUNTY: 130 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. It's gone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:56.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cyborg" Franky-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!\N94 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little short!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:01.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"CYBORG" FRANKY -\N BOUNTY: 94 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:01.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,\Nthe picture is General Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:05.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,God Usopp-{\i1}senpai{\i0}! 200 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:08.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GOD USOPP -\N BOUNTY: 200 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unmasked and\Nthe price is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be targeted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:13.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But the picture is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:18.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, screw you!\NHow did your bounty get so high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my own friend's trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:26.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who is less than 100 million!\NIt's so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still Nami and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:35.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black-Foot" Sanji-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!\N177 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:39.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, his poster isn't a drawing anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:39.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"BLACK-FOOT" SANJI -\N BOUNTY: 177 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:43.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! That's boring. The last one was funnier.
